	<reader oae-label="Reading text (optional)." oae-type="textarea" oae-rows="10">
		<![CDATA[<b>People and Their Clothes</b>

Hello. I’m Ryan Hale, and I’m a banker from Miami. Today is Tuesday, and this evening at 7:00 my favorite restaurant--Food, Music, Love--has a concert. They have great concerts there on Tuesdays, and the restaurant is right around the corner. I have a special tie for these concerts—a tie with pictures of singers. It’s a little crazy, but I really like that tie. The concerts at Food, Music, Love are a little formal, so I need a jacket too. What time is it? Oh, no! It’s already 6:00, and I’m late! 

Ryan Hale
Banker
Miami, United States]]>
	</reader>
